==English==
===Pronunciation===
IPA: /stɪnt/
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪnt|-ɪnt]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# a [[period]] of [[time]]
#:Example:  He had a stint in jail.
# Any of several very small [[wading bird]]s in the genus ''[[Calidris]]''.

[[Category:Birds]]

===Intransitive verb===
{{en-verb}}

# use or give [[too]] [[little]] of something necessary
# (with ''on'':) use or give too little of
#* The next party you throw, don't stint on the beer.


